description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 43, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 43, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Nine Lives for East, Stringalong for South, and 3 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10431-69730-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [43 Votes, Common]
